---------- get or set data to database with now look ( upper , lower  ) ----------

1 - make model and migrate 

2- in model   ( strtoupper , strtolower ,  ucfirst , .... )
 
    protected function Name(): Attribute            // Name -> is the name of column
    {
        return Attribute::make(
            get: fn ($value) => strtolower($value),    // to get data from DB as lower
            set: fn ($value) => strtoupper($value),   // to set data to DB as upper

        );
    }

we should don't forget import attribute page

-  use Illuminate\Database\Eloquent\Casts\Attribute;